{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/create-grids-within-grids","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Tengeneza mitandao ndani ya mitandao","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Konverzija elementa u mrežu utiče samo na svojstva njegovog direktnog roditelja. Stoga, konvertovanjem direktnog roditelja u mrežu, dobijate mrežu unutar mreže.</p>\n<p>Na primer, postavljanjem atributa <code>display</code> i <code>grid-template-columns</code> za element sa klasom <code>item3</code>, kreirate mrežu unutar vaše mreže.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a94fe8569fb03452672e464","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Promeni element sa klasom <code>item3</code> u strukturalnu mrežu sa dve redne širine od <code>auto</code> i <code>1fr</code>, koristeći <code>display</code> i <code>grid-template-columns</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301128,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/create-grids-within-grids"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  .container {\r\n    font-size: 1.5em;\r\n    min-height: 300px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: LightGray;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;\r\n    grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;\r\n    grid-gap: 10px;\r\n    grid-template-areas:\r\n      'advert header'\r\n      'advert content'\r\n      'advert footer';\r\n  }\r\n  .item1 {\r\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\r\n    grid-area: header;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .item2 {\r\n    background: LightSalmon;\r\n    grid-area: advert;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\r\n    grid-area: content;\r\n    /* Only change code below this line */\r\n\r\n\r\n    /* Only change code above this line */\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .item4 {\r\n    background: lightpink;\r\n    grid-area: footer;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .itemOne {\r\n    background: PaleGreen;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .itemTwo {\r\n    background: BlanchedAlmond;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"item1\">header</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item2\">advert</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item3\">\r\n    <div class=\"itemOne\">paragraph1</div>\r\n    <div class=\"itemTwo\">paragraph2</div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"item4\">footer</div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Klasa <code>item3</code> mora imati atribut <code>grid-template-columns</code> sa vrednostima <code>auto</code> na <code>1fr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\r\n  code,\r\n  /.item3\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*grid-template-columns\\s*?:\\s*?auto\\s*?1fr\\s*?;[\\s\\S]*}/gi\r\n);"},{"text":"<p>Klasa <code>item3</code> treba da ima svojstvo <code>display</code> sa vrednošću <code>grid</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /.item3\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*display\\s*?:\\s*?grid\\s*?;[\\s\\S]*}/gi);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-grid","dashedName":"create-grids-within-grids","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-grid","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comment-your-javascript-code","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-media-queries-to-create-responsive-layouts","id":"5a94fe8569fb03452672e464","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"ind